--- CODE CHANGES REQUIRED FOR GCP DEPLOYMENT ---
Apply these minimal changes to gg-cms/backend/go-cms/ before deploying.

=== Change 1: pkg/config/config.go ===
Add Cloud Run PORT injection at the top of the Load() function.
Cloud Run sets the PORT env var; the backend must respect it.

FIND (around line 67, just before viper.AutomaticEnv()):
---
func Load() *Config {
	viper.AutomaticEnv()
---

REPLACE WITH:
---
func Load() *Config {
	// Cloud Run injects PORT — respect it over SERVER_PORT default
	if port := os.Getenv("PORT"); port != "" {
		os.Setenv("SERVER_PORT", port)
	}
	viper.AutomaticEnv()
---

Also add "os" to the import block:
---
import (
	"log"
	"os"

	"github.com/spf13/viper"
)
---


